{"tid":1543783,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府廣告將會在澳洲、北美洲、歐洲和亞洲主要報章刊載","createTime":"2019-09-05T10:15:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T16:49:23.000Z","uid":217254,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dba80964a37bd5f2307615aab8a80fa39c86ae36","tid":1543783,"uid":217254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:15:43.000Z","msg":"Source: HK01<br />\n修例風波持續，網民多次眾籌於海外報章登廣告。據《彭博》報道，香港政府於澳洲時間周四（5日）出版的《澳洲金融評論報》（Australian Financial Review）刊登全版廣告，表示大眾看到的示威新聞，只是在錯綜複雜的社會、經濟和政治拼圖中的其中一塊，強調香港會自行解決問題，毫無疑問會復原，一向如是（We will no doubt bounce back. We always do.）。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人回覆指，有關廣告會在未來一、兩周於澳洲、北美洲、歐洲和亞洲的主要報章刊載，當中首個廣告今日在《澳洲金融評論報》刊載；發言人又指，現時是適當時機由特區政府以真誠、坦率的態度，向國際社會講解政府的看法。<span style=\"color: red;\">不過發言人未回應會於多少份報章登廣告，亦未透露所涉金額。</span><br />\n<br />\n擅用納稅人既錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實需唔需要經立法會財委<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣組做野，所有人都可以係文宣組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e340ba67f5de1beefec01a2dfe768fe3d2bfb90","tid":1543783,"uid":226569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:38:44.000Z","msg":"保護在澳香港學生please<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地翻香港既人身安全已經係個Question Mark<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAlso 英藉港人 and Their 後代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>Protect the pro-democracy Hongkongers in Australia</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/prime-minister-mr-scott-morrison-protect-the-pro-democracy-hongkongers-in-australia?utm_content=bandit-starter_cl_share_content_en-au%3Av12&amp;recruited_by_id=f7fe5230-8c97-11e8-a0c0-bfb104ace612&amp;recruiter=889993192&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=copylink&amp;utm_campaign=share_petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fprime-minister-mr-